text: Martín Palacios Calderón (born 15 March 1972) is a Mexican politician from the Labor Party. In 2012 he served as Deputy of the LXI Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing the State of Mexico. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from the State of Mexico Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Labor Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
